| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0447 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 15583590-c2d8-59ab-91a5-b0ea139351da"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
